  array('id' => '262','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Patrick Chung','dob' => '1987-08-19','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Patrick Chung must have one the most colorful family backgrounds in the NFL. His mother, Sophia George, was a Jamaican singer known for the 1985 reggae hit “Girlie Girlie”; his father, Ronald “Piggy” Chung, produced the song, which became so huge in England it landed young George on Top of the Pops. His brother, as it turns out, is a well-known choreographer and ballet professor (yes, ballet professor). Chung, who enrolled in college at the University of Oregon at age 16, grew up in Snoop Dogg’s adopted hometown of Rancha Cucamonga, Calif., of all places. Patrick Christopher Chung is a Jamaican born American football safety for the New England Patriots of the National Football League. He was drafted by the Patriots in the second round of the 2009 NFL Draft. He played college football at Oregon','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'patrick-chung'),
  array('id' => '263','region_id' => '1','title' => 'Jonathan Vilma','dob' => '1982-04-16','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Like many of the players on this list, Vilma hails from South Florida (Coral Gables) and attended school at the University of Miami. A three-time Pro Bowl selection, the former New York Jet was one of the defensive leaders for the New Orleans Saints team that won the 2010 Super Bowl.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'jonathan-vilma'),
  array('id' => '264','region_id' => '1','title' => 'Jason Pierre-Paul','dob' => '1989-01-01','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'The 6&#8243;5 Jason Pierre-Paul didn’t start playing football until his junior year of high school, after a leg injury sidetracked his basketball career. Now, at 23, he’s one of the most important parts of a resurgent Giants defense which has crushed opposing offenses during its run to the Super Bowl. The second-year defensive end was named First Team All-Pro—in other words, the best player at his position this year','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'jason-pierre-paul'),
  array('id' => '265','region_id' => '4','title' => 'Aaron Hernandez','dob' => '1989-11-06','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Athletes','description' => 'With most football teams, sprightly wide receivers are the quarterback’s go-to guys. But, along with Rob Gronkowski, Aaron Hernandez is part of Tom Brady’s dynamic duo of tight ends (For you non-football people, that’s a larger receiver, who’s job also involves blocking). This season, the duo collectively set NFL records for yardage, receptions, and touchdowns by tight ends on one team, combining for 169 receptions, 2,237 yards, and 24 touchdowns.','video' => 'Football, athlete, nfl,','image' => '','tags' => 'NFL, CT, New England Patriots, Patriots, Bristol, Tight end, NFL draft 2010','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '2015-04-11','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '2014-06-17 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'aaron-hernandez'),
  array('id' => '266','region_id' => '4','title' => 'Victor Cruz','dob' => '1986-11-11','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Athletes','description' => 'The Giants’ improbable run to the Super Bowl owes a whole lot to wide receiver Victor Cruz, who has emerged from complete obscurity before this year to become the team’s all-time record holder for most receiving yards in a season. Half Puerto Rican and half African American, the crowd-pleasing Cruz is perhaps best known for his salsa-dance endzone celebration, which he says is a tribute to his PR-born grandmother. Cruuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuuz, as he’s known in the Meadowlands, is up there with Tim Tebow as one of the most exciting young players to watch in the NFL and, even with just one season under his belt, is more than deserving of the title of NFL’s best Caribbean player','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => 'Football, NFL, Giants, Super Bowl,  wide receiver, all-time record holder ,','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'victor-cruz'),
  array('id' => '267','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Patrice Roberts','dob' => '1986-04-14','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'With hits such as “Islands,” “Band of the Year” and “Tempa Wine” to her credit, Patrice Roberts is one of Trinidad’s most successful female soca artistes. The 27 year old is the headline female of Machel Montano’s HD crew but, but she was actually shining long before she teamed up with the Minister of Road. A second cousin to another legend, Bunji Garlin, soca is clearly in Patrice’s DNA, and sex appeal is pumping through her veins. From her youthful Asian features to her toned form, Patrice is known for her fresh fashion sense, sexy lyrics, and even sexier performances supported by powerful vocals. The diva’s latest album Somebody drops later this month and tracks such as “Doh Rough Meh Up” and “Pong It”are already heating up the charts. Catch the video for “Pong It,” in which Roberts looks for the guy with the right ‘hammer’ to ‘pong it up for her','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'patrice-roberts'),
  array('id' => '268','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Renee Bhagwandeen','dob' => '1988-10-08','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Born in Trinidad but raised in South Florida, this beauty queen-turned-model won the Miss Trinidad International title in 2011 before turning up on America’s Next Top Model Cycle #20 last year. Renee’s most notable asset might be her near-flawless skin, an attribute which has landed her on the cover of wellness magazine New You‘s “Skin” issue.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'renee-bhagwandeen'),
  array('id' => '269','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Teri-Leigh Bovell','dob' => '1983-01-10','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Model','description' => 'Now working behind the scenes as a producer on Caribbean’s Next Top Model , Teri-Leigh Bovell previously played the “vixen” role in music videos by Pharrell, The Game, Rupee and Robin Thicke. She also had a small role in the 2012 film Home Again and been hoisted like a treasure by Richard Branson in some sort of pirate-themed PR campaign/stunt. But in Trinidad she’s probably best known as the longtime girlfriend of soca star Kes. The two finally tied the knot in 2012; a wise move on Kes’ part—we haven’t seen a bad picture of Teri yet.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => 'Caribbean’s Next Top Model, vixen, Kes,','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 05:58:29','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'teri-leigh-bovell'),
  array('id' => '270','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Fay-Ann Lyons-Alvarez','dob' => '1980-11-05','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Before she became wife to soca icon and Soul Train Award winner Bunji Garlin, soca royalty Fay-Ann was the girl that had the men drooling and the women hitting the gym. Yes, she was that hot. Now, she is even hotter. How does she do it? We have no idea. Her fearless style choices have us constantly wondering what she is going to hit us with next, while her physique, confidence level, vocals and smile leave us in awe of this bombshell soca performer. By the way, Fay-Ann is now in the process of studying pole dancing at Trinidad’s premiere erotic workout centre, Provocative Fitness. We can only imagine what she’s coming with for Carnival 2014. Talk about sexiness in overdrive.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'fay-ann-lyons-alvarez'),
  array('id' => '271','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Gabriele Walcott','dob' => '1984-06-26','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Beauty queen/model Gabrielle “Gabby” Walcott has represented Trinidad in both the Miss World and Miss Universe pageants, placing second runner-up for the former in 2008, and winning Miss Caribbean World title. Her resume also includes appearan es in Rupee’s “Tempted to Touch” and Robin Thicke’s “Wanna Love U Girl” videos and, most curiously, set design work for MTV’s Real World/Road Rules Challenge: The Gauntlet.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'gabriele-walcott'),
  array('id' => '272','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Desha Rambhajan','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Journalist','description' => 'Almost every night at around seven in T&T you can catch Desha Rambhajan on the local CTV news broadcast but, trust me, people aren’t just tuning in for the weather report. One would assume beautiful would suffice in describing this local treasure but it hardly gets the job done. From newspaper and spreads and fashion editorials to our TV screens, her captivating voice and striking features leaves no doubt in our minds that Desha deserves to be among the top in this lis','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => 'Trinidad, Tobago, Newscaster, Journalist','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'desha-rambhajan'),
  array('id' => '273','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Lola Monroe','dob' => '1986-10-25','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'This one was something of a surprise. While most would chalk Angel Melaku aka Lola Monroe’s exotic looks up to her Ethiopian birth, it turns out she’s of mixed Ethiopian and Trinidadian parentage. We knew there was something about this chesty video-chick-turned-rapper that was more than meets the eye.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'lola-monroe'),
  array('id' => '274','region_id' => '5','title' => 'Sintra Arunte-Bronte','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'The iconic image of a voluptuous vixen sporting a wet red t-shirt has been a staple of Jamaican tourism since 1972. It’s no doubt that her image has encouraged many to visit the island with hopes of finding their own buxom beauty. Little known is that the lady in red is actually a Trini, Sintra Arunte-Bronte, who was discovered while standing outside of the Jamaica Pegasus hotel. As a result of that famous photo, a race horse, boat and a Swiss watch have all been named after her. Presently, Sintra runs A.J.M. Tours in Trinidad with her husband, providing charter services between Trinidad, New York and Tobago. Though it’s been over 40 years since that photograph, it’s been said she still possesses the beauty that caught the eye of that photographer so many years ago.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'sintra-arunte-bronte'),
  array('id' => '275','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Orlando Franklin','dob' => '1987-04-12','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Franklin was born in Montego Bay, and moved to Toronto with his mother at age 3. Growing up in Canada, he developed an interest in football and was recruited by the University of Miami. Since graduating he’s been a starter with the Broncos offense, which is rated number 1 in the country, thanks in no small part to the offensive linemen allowing Manning to work in his mysterious (but all-too-effective) ways. Even Rob Ford (current mayor of Franklin’s hometown and apparent Jamaicaphile) is getting behind Franklin as he heads into the Super Bowl. Look out for Franklin this weekend as you watch — big ups to him for making it all the way!','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'orlando-franklin'),
  array('id' => '276','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Tosh Alexander','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Singer','description' => 'You know that fiesty Jamaican girl talking trash at the beginning of Busta Rhymes’ latest single, “Twerk It”? That’s Tosh Alexander. Yeah, we hadn’t heard of her, either, until the song dropped, but ever since following her Instagram feed and catching a glimpse of her in action in the “Twerk It” video, we’ve been smitten with the up-and-coming vocalist with the girl-next-door looks. We’re looking forward to seeing more of her—especially with that cute  bob haircut she’s sporting now.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => 'Singer, twerk it,','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'tosh-alexander'),
  array('id' => '277','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Shelly-Ann Fraser Pryce','dob' => '1986-12-27','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'There’s much to admire about two-time Olympic gold-medalist Shelly Ann Fraser Pryce’s athletic accomplishments, but watch one of her races with enough men around, and you’re sure to hear as many complements on her long legs and sweet smile as her finish times. Curious whether she looks as good in street clothes as she does in a sweaty track suit? See her recent appearance on BET’s 106 and Park.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'shelly-ann-fraser-pryce'),
  array('id' => '278','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Gaye McDonald','dob' => '0000-10-19','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Stunning is the only way to describe the look of 24-year-old model Gaye McDonald. Her visibility has diminished recently, after an early career that saw her win 2005&#8242;s Caribbean Model Search, cover Luire magazine (in 2007) and appear in French and Italian Vogue editorials and campaigns for Nordstrom and Benetton, but her good looks haven’t waned. Sure, things have been quiet for her of late, but when you look this pretty, opportunities are always around the corner.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'gaye-mcdonald'),
  array('id' => '279','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Jodie Smith','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'We’ve been checking for British-born, LA-based Jamaican model Jodie Smith ever since her nude pictorial in Pop Africana magazine drew our attention to her flawless skin and stunningly long body. (Yes, this girl’s a bit of an exhibitionist, as a quick visit to her Instagram will attest). Having already taken the fashion world by storm, she’s recently branched out with roles in the latest season of True Blood (as one of three bloody, naked “sirens” stalking Bill Compton) and the mystery girl in 2 Chainz and Pharrell’s new “Feds Watching” video. She doesn’t have speaking lines in either, but fortunately she’s got the kind of body that does nuff talking. With a look and bold personality that recalls a young Grace Jones, we see action-movie and femme fatale roles in her future. Don’t sleep on Miss Jodie (as she prefers to be called), and remember where you heard it first.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:15:47','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'jodie-smith'),
  array('id' => '280','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Jaunel McKenzie','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'She’s whip-smart, doe-eyed and bowlegged with a strut like no other, leaving many in her wake to stop and say “wow” (trust us, we’ve seen it). Her exotic look and undeniable allure anchored her as she won Pulse Caribbean Model Search 2002, moving on to not only become the Caribbean’s most successful black model, but, at one time, the number one black model in the world! Appearing in nearly the entire catalog of Vogue magazines, Marie Claire, Glamour, Elle, Cosmopolitan, Pirelli and a multiplicity of Daily Front Row covers—the official newspaper of New York Fashion Week— is no small feat, and if you thought that was it, phew! Declared one of the most successful black models of all time by Ebony in 2008, she was also named one of the 100 most influential black people by Vibe. There’s no debating that McKenzie is a stunner, but just in case you weren’t convinced, check out her Essence spread alongside John Legend. We rest our case.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'jaunel-mckenzie'),
  array('id' => '281','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Gina Hargitay','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'This mixed-heritage teenaged beauty (she’s Jamaican and Hungarian) will be vying for the ‘Beauty with a Purpose’ title in Jakarta, Indonesia next month, and is already getting lots of attention on the international level. Why, you ask? At just over 18 Miss Jamaica World possesses a confidence and eloquence almost beyond her years. She’s intelligent, magnetic, and really passionate about her country, which is great… especially when paired with a beautiful face and awesome body.  Now the clich&eacute;d question on everyone’s lips is “could she be the next Lisa Hanna?” We certainly think so.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'gina-hargitay'),
  array('id' => '283','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Taneish \\"Lava\\" Simpson','dob' => '1985-10-10','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'TV Star','description' => 'Taneish is not by any means the most popular on our list, but if you haven’t already acquainted yourself with this incredibly sexy yahdie diva, now is the time. We got first glimpse of the feisty model when she appeared on VH-1’s reality TV dating series For The Love Of Ray J and, after the season, she made headlines when she dated Usain Bolt in 2010. Fast forward to today, and she’s getting her Amber Rose on with a new close-cropped haircut and looking hotter than ever. She’s always oozed sex appeal and commanded gawks and stares but now, she is definitely turning it up. It’s a good look!','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => 'VH1, For The Love Of Ray J , reality tv,','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'taneish-lava-simpson'),
  array('id' => '284','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Jeneil Williams','dob' => '1990-02-25','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'You’ve certainly seen her before, you must have… after all, she’s currently KILLING the fashion industry. LOVE magazine? Vogue? i-D? Harper’s Bazaar? Pirelli calendar? How about campaigns for Louis Vuitton, Balenciaga, Benetton and Jimmy Choo? Check, check and check again… but we won’t bother to take on another exhaustive list of accomplishments. It’s easy to see why too, there is not a single bad picture of this woman (dare you to find one!) She’s intelligent, driven and super-humble, which is itself an achievement given her impressive career. Plus the industry often makes reference to her dark chocolate hue, “personality, legs and lip” as the perfect it girl package. Jeneil Williams is sexy not just for being sexy, but for embracing her uniqueness too… something about her is bound to pull you in. She just had to make our list!','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'jeneil-williams'),
  array('id' => '285','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Jamelia','dob' => '1981-01-11','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'This lovely gyal born ah farin in Birmingham, England first came to public attention in 2000 with her debut album Drama featuring the single “So High” and “Money” with Beenie Man. Though still best known as a singer (and primarily known in the UK versus the US and Jamaica), she’s also ventured into modeling (for Reebok, among others, and at Naomi Campbell’s Fashion for Relief runway show) and acting, most recently in the Caribbean-set BBC drama Death in Paradise.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'jamelia'),
  array('id' => '286','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Lois Samuels','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Striking features, big smile and absolute poise… there was no doubt the statuesque Lois Samuels was destined for greatness. The supermodel boasts a remarkable list of achievements and continues to make her presence felt as a fashion designer for her clothing line, The Vessel. After being discovered in high school and winning Jamaican agency Pulse’s model search in 1991, Samuels found success with Calvin Klein’s ‘CK One’ advertising campaign, and was soon strutting Parisian runways for a slew of big-name labels. She became the first-ever Vogue cover girl from the Caribbean, opening the door for many other Caribbean belles to make their mark. Years later, even after marriage and children, the exotic beauty barely looks a day older.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'lois-samuels'),
  array('id' => '287','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Nell Robinson','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Nell Robinson burst onto the scene with her wide eyes, amazing figure, perfect breasts and gazelle-like gait, winning Pulse’s first Supermodel of the Caribbean competition in 2002. Her career has been on a roll ever since, and for good reason—there’s just something special about the top model. Nell was declared ‘The Body’ of the year by Arena magazine when she appeared on its cover in 2005, and has also showcased her signature features in GQ Italy, Vogue, Cosmopolitan, Allure and Trace. She’s also scored gigs with high-end brands like Abercrombie &amp; Fitch, J-Lo, Victoria’s Secret and Agent Provocateur. She recently debuted her own Bang! swimwear line to rave reviews, and now that Rihanna posted a #selfie on her Instagram account wearing one, we’re eagerly anticipating this stunner’s next venture.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'nell-robinson'),
  array('id' => '288','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Sanya Hughes','dob' => '1982-10-03','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'We first got a glimpse of Sanya Hughes when she won Pulse’s Petite Jamaica Fashion Model and the Miss Jamaica Universe competition in 2002. When she was voted as the sexiest woman in North America and the Caribbean later that year, we knew we’d be seeing a lot more of her. Contracts with Elite Model Management in Miami and LA Talent in Los Angeles followed suit, making her the only petite Pulse model to go on to an international modelling career. Now based in L.A., Hughes has appeared in soul music legend George Michael’s “Amazing” music video, worked with a bevy of high-end labels and ripped runways all over, becoming the face of Bare Minerals ad campaign in the USA and Sephora stores in the U.K. She also played The Mermaid in Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides alongside Johnny Depp and Penelope Cruz. No small feat for the alluring, driven beauty. Naturally, we’re watching to see what her next move will be.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'sanya-hughes'),
  array('id' => '289','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Carla Campbell','dob' => '1981-07-11','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Model','description' => 'Probably best known for her appearance in the 2006 edition of the Sports Illustrated swimsuit issue, in which (let’s be honest here) she stood out in part thanks to her remarkable combination of large natural breasts and otherwise taut, athletic frame, Carla Campbell has broken a number of barriers during her decade-plus-long career. Not only was she the first Caribbean-born model to appear in that most iconic of magazine special editions, but she was also only the second island gyal to model for Victoria’s Secret. While her chest often receives all of the attention, we submit that her greatest asset might actually be those doe eyes. Just try not to get lost in them.','video' => '','image' => '1404849278201203291159318319.jpg','tags' => 'model, sports illustrated, Victoria Secret,','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '4','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '2015-05-07','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:23:44','postdate' => '2014-08-06 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => 'Victoria Secret Model ','twittershortdesc' => '','slug' => 'carla-campbell'),
  array('id' => '290','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Esther Anderson','dob' => '1946-08-04','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Others','description' => 'Not to dwell on this Bob Marley side gyal thing, but Bob knew how to pick ‘em. Point in case: the breathtaking and talented Esther Anderson, who briefly dated Marley during the pivotal year of 1973. More than just a romantic partner, Anderson was a key player in the early incarnation of Island Records, acting as the label’s publicity director, and taking some of the most photographs of the iconic singer. The multi-talented Anderson went on to work as a dancer, actress and film director after relocating from Jamaica to England, starring alongside Sidney Poitier in 1973&#8242;s A Warm December, a role that won her an NAACP Image Award for Best Actress.','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => '','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:39:25','postdate' => '0000-00-00 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'esther-anderson'),
  array('id' => '291','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Beryl Cunningham','dob' => '0000-00-00','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Entrepreneur','description' => 'OK, for this last one we thought we’d leave you with someone a little more obscure. In fact, we doubt there are many people in Jamaica even who’ve heard of Montego Bay-born Beryl Cunningham. But she was a sex symbol in Italy, where she starred in numerous B-movies during the ’60s and ’70s (after marrying director Piero Vivarelli), appearing nude in just about all of them, it appears. Want to see more of this vintage movie kitten? Here she is in a very out-there striptease scene from 1969&#8242;s evocatively titled Cosi Dolce… Cosi Perversa','video' => '','image' => '','tags' => 'actress, model. singer','facebook' => '','twitter' => '','facebookfanpage' => '','twitterfanpage' => '','instagram' => '','status' => '1','admin_id' => '1','conform' => '0','modifydate' => '0000-00-00','createdate' => '2014-06-13 06:39:25','postdate' => '2014-07-08 00:00:00','rejectreason' => '','shortdesc' => NULL,'twittershortdesc' => NULL,'slug' => 'beryl-cunningham'),
