  array('id' => '658','region_id' => '2','title' => 'Gloria Reuben','dob' => '1964-06-09','kind' => 'People profile','category' => 'Actress','description' => 'Reuben was born in Toronto, to a classical singer mother and an architect father.[1] Her father is White Canadian and her mother is Jamaican.[2][3][4] Reuben is the half-sister of Denis Simpson, an actor and children\\\'s television host who died in 2010.[2] She began learning piano as a child and studied later music technique and theory, ballet and jazz at the Canadian Royal Conservatory.[3] Her career as an actress was triggered by a few jobs as a model and TV ad appearances.

